      <title>微软发布安全公告3046310：关于不当签发数字证书导致身份伪造的风险</title>
      <link>https://qife122.github.io/p/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A3046310%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%93%E7%AD%BE%E5%8F%91%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E8%AF%81%E4%B9%A6%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E4%BC%AA%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9/</link>
